{"tid":149712,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"再續情緣 朱千雪客串《踩過界》披婚紗嫁王浩信","createTime":"2017-03-09T12:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T23:50:28.000Z","uid":9573,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e5cbe0d88c6ec231680e1fc59df7775e5487255","tid":149712,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T12:54:20.000Z","msg":"民選冠軍朱千雪因為甜美的外貌和爽朗的性格深得觀眾的喜愛。上年她和王浩信合演的電視劇「EU超時任務」備受網民的追捧，螢幕情侶的形象深入民心。今年，一向有自己想法和好學的﻿麗湖居獲9800元承租朱千雪因為要修讀法律博士的課程，會減少拍劇的數量，觀眾可能不能常常在電視中見到她的身影了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/18b0000049dbda4627aa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F18b0000049dbda4627aa&h=21ec09e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但沒關係，朱千雪會於TVB的新劇「踩過界」客串一角，更會與王浩信再續前緣。據聞在劇中，朱千雪會飾演﻿淺月灣盡享悠閒生活王浩信的初戀情人。日前拍攝一幕二人分離的場面，朱千雪痛哭離開。雖然千雪已經盡力把哭的表情演譯出來，但奈何沒有眼淚，最後要靠眼藥水的幫助。除此之外，朱千雪更拍攝了一場穿婚紗的戲份，只見她仙氣十足，笑容依舊甜美。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/x7cZkeqLUVNeX9ZOydgkdg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/f895d2f8b21bbeaf3df587322240a247\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fx7cZkeqLUVNeX9ZOydgkdg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2Ff895d2f8b21bbeaf3df587322240a247&h=db2c2d26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QtDB_YlGHfbm4bgcZawDeA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/eb43059968626d3952b5423e81822180\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FQtDB_YlGHfbm4bgcZawDeA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2Feb43059968626d3952b5423e81822180&h=76be95b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/